    <item>
      <title>西撒哈拉的冻结冲突即将结束吗？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/western-sahara-is-the-frozen-conflict-nearing-an-end</link>
      <description><![CDATA[1975 年，殖民大国西班牙放弃了西撒哈拉，摩洛哥趁机占领该地。在摩洛哥邻国阿尔及利亚的支持下，部分撒哈拉土著居民起义反抗新统治者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/western-sahara-is-the-frozen-conflict-nearing-an-end</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 14:35:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Uber 将核实乘客身份，以加强驾驶员安全</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/uber-to-verify-passengers-identities-as-part-of-driver-safety-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[为了让司机感到更安全，Uber Technologies Inc. 将开始根据第三方身份验证数据库检查乘客的账户信息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/uber-to-verify-passengers-identities-as-part-of-driver-safety-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 14:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃森哲将大部分晋升计划推迟六个月</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/accenture-to-delay-bulk-of-promotions-by-six-months-on-outlook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃森哲公司 (Accenture Plc) 计划将大部分员工的晋升推迟六个月，这是咨询业长期低迷的最新迹象，对整个咨询业造成了影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-17/accenture-to-delay-bulk-of-promotions-by-six-months-on-outlook</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 17 Sep 2024 14:06:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
